

=Bio=

"I'm a horticulturist. My work involves ethnobotany, social justice & agroecology. Vivo en California Norte y Mexico Sur.

I design landscapes from broadacre to kitchen gardens scale. I teach seed saving at the bay area seed interchange library. My growing climates are mediterranean and semiarid climates USDA zones 8 & 9. I am working on breeding open pollenating crops for cool costal climates."


